      "content": "i just don't get it. you keep calling it \"common-sense\" like there's no actual debate. if a lot of people and legal experts believe these laws violate the constitution and infringe on their rights, isn't that a valid perspective? why are you framing one side as \"dangerous misreading\" while treating the other side as just the objective \"truth\"?",
